{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "software_management", "channel": "software_licenses", "user": "johndoe", "message": "Reminder for the team: we are having a meeting tomorrow to discuss the new software updates. Please come prepared with your thoughts and concerns.", "created_at": 1620500000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "asset_management", "channel": "vehicle_components", "user": "janedoe", "message": "I've noticed a minor issue with one of our battery components. I'm working with the supplier to resolve it. Will update you all once it's sorted.", "created_at": 1620500000001}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "asset_management", "channel": "vehicle_components", "user": "oliviamartinez", "message": "Thanks for the update, Jane. Please keep us posted on the progress.", "created_at": 1620500000002}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "software_management", "channel": "software_licenses", "user": "oliviamartinez", "message": "John, could you please update us on the budget allocation for the next quarter's software purchases?", "created_at": 1620500000003}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "software_management", "channel": "software_licenses", "user": "johndoe", "message": "Sure Olivia, I'm currently finalizing the figures. I will share the details in our next meeting.", "created_at": 1620500000004}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "asset_management", "channel": "vehicle_components", "user": "janedoe", "message": "I've received an update from the supplier. The battery issue should be resolved by next week. Will keep you all posted.", "created_at": 1620500000005}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "software_management", "channel": "software_licenses", "user": "johndoe", "message": "Hello Team, just to let you all know, we have successfully integrated the new software license management system that includes predictive alerts for expiring licenses. This update has been issued across all Elexion Automotive divisions. This should help us better manage our software assets and avoid any unexpected disruptions due to expired licenses.", "create_at": 1632969600000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "software_management", "channel": "software_licenses", "user": "oliviamartinez", "message": "That's great news, John! Just to confirm, has this predictive alert system been implemented across our manufacturing divisions as well?", "create_at": 1632973200000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "software_management", "channel": "software_licenses", "user": "johndoe", "message": "Yes, Olivia. The predictive alerts for expiring software licenses have been activated across all divisions, including our manufacturing units. If there are any further queries or concerns, feel free to discuss.", "create_at": 1632976800000}}
